# UI upgrade mandatory — FIRST CHECK always (general + per-app ledger)

**General law:** `brain-os/law/enforcement/SOURCEA_UI_UPGRADE_MANDATORY_PROCESS_LOCKED_v1.md`  
**FIRST CHECK wire:** `.cursor/rules/025-ui-upgrade-first-check-live-wire.mdc` (alwaysApply)  
**Per-app ledgers:** `data/ui-upgrade-ledgers-index-v1.json`  
**Ledger script:** `scripts/ui_upgrade_ledger_v1.py`  
**Landing sub-law:** `.cursor/rules/023-ui-upgrade-no-downgrade.mdc`  
**Form sub-law:** `.cursor/rules/form-automatic-submit-only.mdc`

## Hard rule (founder locked)

> **FIRST CHECK before ANY UI edit — form, app, website, hub, canvas. Machine blocks writes without ack.**

```bash
python3 scripts/ui_upgrade_path_classifier_v1.py --path "<file>" --json
python3 scripts/ui_upgrade_first_check_v1.py --surface <id> --ack --json
```

## Founder trigger

**up** · **UI upgrade** · **upgrade UI** · **redesign** · **polish UI** → run **both layers** before any HTML/CSS/JS edit.

## Two layers (both mandatory)

| Layer | What |
|-------|------|
| **General** | UP-0 … UP-7 — same for every app |
| **Per-app** | That app's frozen inventory + app checklist + upgrade history |

```bash
python3 scripts/ui_upgrade_ledger_v1.py --surface <id> --show --json   # read last version
python3 scripts/ui_upgrade_mandatory_gate_v1.py --surface <id> --print-checklist
```

