## Pipeline

```text
READ general UP-0..UP-7
READ per-app ledger — frozen inventory + app checklist + last upgrade
INVENTORY last version vs frozen inventory
EDIT additive only
VERIFY general + app machine gates
APPEND upgrade entry to ledger JSON + MD history
PASTE ship summary — preserved · changed · achieved · quality vs last · founder approval
```

## Ship summary required fields

- General checklist UP-0..UP-7 PASS  
- **App-specific checklist** PASS (from that app's ledger)  
- **Preserved table** — every frozen inventory item before/after  
- **Changed** — what moved/added  
- **Achieved** — quality outcome  
- **quality_vs_last:** `same` or `better` — never `downgraded`  
- **founder_approval:** pending/approved  
- **upgrade_id** appended to ledger

## Forbidden

- Upgrade without reading that app's ledger first  
- Ship without appending ledger entry  
- Downgrade (missing frozen inventory item) without `UI BASELINE BUMP`

